==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transmissionist
<hw>Trans*mis"sion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An adherent of a theory,
the <col><b>transmission theory</b></col>, that the brain serves to
⟦ldquo⟧transmit,⟦rdquo⟧ rather than to originate, conclusions, and hence
that consciousness may exist independently of the brain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transmissive</ent>⟦br⟧
